title: League of Legends not Opening
body: I play league on a mac, no wonder its not working. When I click the league icon nothing happens at all. In the dock when i click league or use spotlight, the league icon would usually pop up but all it does is move the dock a bit then do nothing. Please fix Riot its not fun having nothing to do...

replies.body:

Have you tried it with heightened privileges?
